name: Recycled aluminium  flower wind chimes
description:
These amazing wind chimes are hand made from recycled pots and pans in Tanzania. 

They can be hung indoors or outside and make a light clinking noise in the breeze. 

The heartwarming project which creates these gorgeous items uses traditional recycling technologies and employes people with physical disabilities greatly increasing their quality of life and assisting them to live a sustainable lifestyle in Tanzania.
